headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Carvana (CVNA) After A 140% One-Year Surge?
summary: If you are wondering whether Carvana's share price really lines up with its underlying value, this article will walk through the key numbers that matter. Carvana's stock closed at US$463.09, with returns of 15.7% over the last week, a 1% decline over the last month, 15.7% year to date and 139.9% over the last year, while the 3 year return is very large and the 5 year return is 61.0%. These sharp moves have kept Carvana in the spotlight, as investors weigh what the recent share price means...
